descriptionHtml:
FXAA Injector Custom Settings-More Colourful and Realistic without Unnecessary Effects

All I\'ve seen with the plugin is people going overboard on the sharpen, vignetting, and color effects. I decided to do a slight tweak to the saturation, tweak to main colors to more of a steel blue, and slightly increase the sharpen. I also disabled all those other silly ugly effects like vignetting, sepia, and Technicolor as they really don\'t do anything but make the game look ugly.
